ozhium-ollium Dependencies
===========================

Build Dependencies
-------------------
  - GCC or Clang compiler
  - pkg-config
  - make

Runtime Dependencies
--------------------
  Daemon (ozhium-ollium):
    - libpulse-dev    (PulseAudio library)
    - libmnl-dev     (netlink library for network/bluetooth/VPN events)

  UI (ozhium-ollium-ui) — choose one backend:
    - Option A (GTK): gtk4, gtk4-layer-shell
    - Option B (Qt):  qt6-base (qt6-base-dev), qt6-declarative (qt6-declarative-dev)

System Requirements
-------------------
  - Linux kernel with inotify and netlink support
  - PulseAudio sound server
  - /sys/class/backlight/    (backlight device paths)
  - /sys/class/power_supply/ (battery device paths)

Installation Examples
---------------------

  Debian/Ubuntu:
    sudo apt install build-essential pkg-config libpulse-dev libmnl-dev libgtk-4-dev libgtk4-layer-shell-dev qt6-base-dev qt6-declarative-dev

  Fedora/RHEL:
    sudo dnf install gcc make pkg-config pulseaudio-libs-devel libmnl-devel gtk4-devel gtk4-layer-shell-devel qt6-qtbase-devel qt6-qtdeclarative-devel

  Arch Linux:
    sudo pacman -S base-devel pkgconf pulseaudio libmnl gtk4 qt6-base qt6-declarative

  openSUSE:
    sudo zypper install gcc make pkg-config libpulse-devel libmnl-devel gtk4-devel gtk4-layer-shell-devel qt6-base-devel qt6-declarative-devel

Verification
------------
  After installation, run:
    make

  This will build both:
    - ozhium-ollium      (daemon)
    - ozhium-ollium-ui  (UI binary)
